1
00:00:29,791 --> 00:00:30,750
What?!

2
00:00:31,583 --> 00:00:32,375
[OKAZAKI, OURA yell]

3
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:33,291
[TSUTOMU grunts]

4
00:00:33,375 --> 00:00:35,250
