So that's what's going on.

55
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,250
Thought so.

56
00:04:11,333 --> 00:04:13,958
Yeah, fine.
We're cooperating. See?

57
00:04:14,041 --> 00:04:15,458
[SOLDIER 21A]
Freeze!

58
00:04:15,541 --> 00:04:16,500
[SOLDIER 21B]
Hey!

59
00:04:17,583 --> 00:04:18,708
[SAKURAKO]
It's all right.

60
00:04:18,791 --> 00:04:21,333
I need you to activate
Vector Two remotely.

61
00:04:21,416 --> 00:04:24,416
Trust me.
Be discreet as possible.

62
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,375
[SHOKO gasps]

63
00:04:25,458 --> 00:04:27,208
[SAKURAKO]
Please.

64
00:04:27,291 --> 00:04:29,375
Why would you
need Aquarion Logos?

65
00:04:29,458 --> 00:04:30,583
Because...

66
00:04:30,666 --> 00:04:32,750
The coming of
Aquarion Logos represents

67
00:04:32,833 --> 00:04:34,541
the end of the world
as we know it!

68
00:04:34,625 --> 00:04:36,958
You're gonna end the world

69
00:04:37,041 --> 00:04:39,375
because of your
grudge against Akira?

70
00:04:39,458 --> 00:04:40,916
