71
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,041
How can you be so selfish?!

72
00:04:43,125 --> 00:04:44,083
[slap]

73
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:49,250
[groans]

74
00:04:49,333 --> 00:04:52,583
I won't be condescended
to by a puppet!

75
00:04:52,666 --> 00:04:54,500
No... Subete, don't.

76
00:04:54,583 --> 00:04:57,541
[SUBETE]
I will outshine Akira!

77
00:04:57,625 --> 00:04:59,291
