113
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:49,541
[TSUTOMU yells]

114
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:54,500
[SHOKO]
Oh, god! Oh, god!

115
00:06:54,583 --> 00:06:55,875
No! Hang in there, sweetie!

116
00:06:55,958 --> 00:06:57,625
Don't you even
think about dying!

117
00:06:58,958 --> 00:07:00,083
[TSUTOMU]
What?

118
00:07:00,166 --> 00:07:03,041
With your boobs touching me?
Not a chance.

119
00:07:03,125 --> 00:07:04,416
Idiot!

120
00:07:05,625 --> 00:07:06,666
Damn...

121
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:08,250
We've done what we could.

122
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:10,041
It's up to Akira now.

123
00:07:10,125 --> 00:07:12,666
We gave him an opening,
launching Vector Two.

124
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,583
