126
00:07:17,875 --> 00:07:19,833
[SAKURAKO] Now, if only
Vector Ga would activate

127
00:07:19,916 --> 00:07:21,875
and start devouring concepts...

128
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:24,125
[AKIRA]
Verbalize.

129
00:07:32,083 --> 00:07:33,875
[SOLDIER 21F] Someone
tell me where I am, please?

130
00:07:33,958 --> 00:07:35,000
[SAKURAKO]
Sick bay, stat!

131
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:36,708
[KENTO]
Get a stretcher over here!

132
00:07:36,791 --> 00:07:37,958
[HAYATO]
Hurry! He's bleeding out!

133
00:07:38,041 --> 00:07:39,458
One look at your eyes
was enough to tell me

134
00:07:39,541 --> 00:07:42,875
