to neutralize its power,

137
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:47,375
or we'll never get through this.

138
00:07:47,458 --> 00:07:49,291
[KENTO]
The monument's our only option.

139
00:07:49,375 --> 00:07:51,583
Vector Ga can't be
activated by computer.

140
00:07:51,666 --> 00:07:55,333
We'll just have to cross our
fingers and have faith in Akira.

141
00:07:55,416 --> 00:07:57,250
[SAKURAKO]
I don't like this gamble,

142
00:07:57,333 --> 00:08:00,083
but your little stunt
has left us no choice.

143
00:08:00,166 --> 00:08:01,291
[KENTO]
I'm sorry.

144
00:08:01,375 --> 00:08:02,375
I'd have tried to warn you,

145
00:08:02,458 --> 00:08:04,000
but they had me
under surveillance.

146
00:08:04,083 --> 00:08:05,208
[beeping noise]

147
00:08:05,291 --> 00:08:07,333
[AKIRA] I'm going on ahead.
I've got this.

148
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:09,500
