152
00:08:12,958 --> 00:08:14,291
It's f-fine.

153
00:08:14,375 --> 00:08:16,583
Shoko and I will
stay with Tsutomu.

154
00:08:16,666 --> 00:08:17,500
Stay strong.

155
00:08:17,583 --> 00:08:19,375
Of c-course.

156
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:21,000
[MAIA]
