have some fun.

164
00:09:13,166 --> 00:09:16,291
Come now. Shall we dance?

165
00:09:29,125 --> 00:09:34,125
[maniacal laughter]

166
00:09:39,333 --> 00:09:41,916
[HAYATO] Are you ever not
going to be a pain in the ass?

167
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,458
[KARAN] We really don't
mind helping, you know.

168
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,875
[MAIA]
Akira!

169
00:09:47,958 --> 00:09:48,958
[AKIRA]
You're late.

170
00:09:49,041 --> 00:09:50,541
