172
00:09:52,708 --> 00:09:53,958
[KARAN, MAIA]
Roger!

173
00:09:54,041 --> 00:09:55,375
[AKIRA]
Genesis Merge.

174
00:09:55,458 --> 00:09:56,750
[MAIA]
Shout it!

175
00:09:56,833 --> 00:09:58,166
[KARAN, HAYATO]
Fly!

176
00:09:58,250 --> 00:10:00,166
[AKIRA, MAIA]
Aquarion!

177
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:02,583
[KARAN, HAYATO]
Aquarion!

178
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:14,541
[AKIRA, MAIA]
San!

