182
00:10:28,083 --> 00:10:29,416
[MAIA]
Subete...

183
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:32,166
[SUBETE] Vector Ga, the machine
that ended the legend.

184
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:34,416
