[MALE DOCTOR 21A]
Lidocaine. Hundred mil.

187
00:10:45,583 --> 00:10:46,625
[MALE STAFF MEMBER 21B]
Where's that donor packet?

188
00:10:46,708 --> 00:10:48,250
