She's gone on the offensive!

209
00:12:09,583 --> 00:12:11,833
[laughing]

210
00:12:19,916 --> 00:12:21,666
Vile chicken scratch!

211
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:25,458
I curse your existence!
You are a blight!

212
00:12:25,541 --> 00:12:28,166
[CROWD screaming]

213
00:12:29,083 --> 00:12:31,041
I have to save them.

214
00:12:31,125 --> 00:12:32,958
I can't let her
do any more damage.

215
00:12:33,041 --> 00:12:34,166
[MAIA gasps]

216
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,625
[AKIRA]
What?

217
00:12:35,708 --> 00:12:36,958
[NESTA]
Very soon.

218
00:12:37,041 --> 00:12:39,125
