Talk to me!

219
00:12:39,208 --> 00:12:40,250
[NESTA]
He will...

220
00:12:40,333 --> 00:12:42,125
[MAIA whimpering]

221
00:12:42,208 --> 00:12:43,833
[AKIRA]
That look on your face...

222
00:12:43,916 --> 00:12:46,416
[garbled voice]
Are you okay? Maia!

223
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,875
[NESTA]
...disappear.

224
00:12:47,958 --> 00:12:48,916
[MAIA]
No...

225
00:12:50,625 --> 00:12:52,583
[MAIA]
No!

226
00:13:00,166 --> 00:13:05,166
[VECTOR GA] Nesta, I shall
devour the very concept of you.

227
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:07,416
