229
00:13:08,875 --> 00:13:10,875
[VECTOR GA]
Devour...

230
00:13:10,958 --> 00:13:14,333
Devour! Devour!

231
00:13:14,416 --> 00:13:17,750
Wait! Don't you
know what's happening?!

232
00:13:17,833 --> 00:13:19,708
