you'll disappear forever!

234
00:13:28,666 --> 00:13:29,875
[AKIRA]
Yeah, so?

235
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:33,125
[MAIA]
You idiot!

236
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:37,666
[M.J.B.K. laughing]

237
00:13:38,916 --> 00:13:40,333
Get out of our way!

238
00:13:40,416 --> 00:13:41,750
Damn.

239
00:13:41,833 --> 00:13:43,000
