the wellspring of my power.

248
00:14:22,958 --> 00:14:23,916
[MAIA gasps]

249
00:14:26,291 --> 00:14:29,208
Akira... Forgive me.

250
00:14:29,291 --> 00:14:30,250
[AKIRA gasps]

251
00:14:32,708 --> 00:14:33,416
[AKIRA]
No!

252
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,875
